Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}雖然是未曾聽聞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:46.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}卻感到無限懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:52.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}只因你在我身旁
